OL,3,CTwelfth of July celebrations begin
OL,5,FThe lighting of bonfires have begun in
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland marking the beginning
OL,7,Fof the Twelfth of July celebrations.
OL,9,FA number of the traditional Eleventh
OL,10,FNight bonfires were lit late on Friday
OL,11,Fwith further pyres to be ignited on
OL,12,FSaturday and Sunday.
OL,14,FA large crowd attended the Corcrain
OL,15,Fbonfire on Friday night in Portadown
OL,16,Fwhere a fireworks display also took
OL,17,Fplace.
OL,19,FThe bonfires are lit ahead of the
OL,20,FOrange Order's July 12 parades across
OL,21,FNorthern Ireland on Monday.
